works.description:
The outline of artwork, as submitted to  

USPTO.  Black and white Circle drawn to resemble a plate, with chain links
 
appearing and within the rim 2 circular lines drawn to resemble a narrow  

band, within that a horizontal type line with 5 plants from seedling to  
mature plant and a bee in the upper portion.  There are two black/white  
drawings (in addition to the color design earlier reported) appearing on  

the website, that have not been authorized.
